## SYSTEM EVOLUTION

v1 → Basic API  
v2 → Frontend separation  
v3 → Task queue  
v4 → Worker system  
v5 → AI pipeline  
v6 → Realtime dashboard  
v7 → SaaS system  
v8 → Billing integration  
v9 → Distributed workers  
v10 → Production architecture  

